official_title: To amend the Internal Revenue Code of 1986 to extend the treatment of qualified small issue bonds through 1996.

summary.text: Amends the Internal Revenue Code to extend the tax exemption for qualified small issue industrial bonds (bonds issued to finance manufacturing facilities and farm property) through 1996.

titles.title: To amend the Internal Revenue Code of 1986 to extend the treatment of qualified small issue bonds through 1996.
